    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195580/extras/ea7621ae89a93123b6531961ea0fddc1.poster.avif?t=1772009947\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195580/extras/ea7621ae89a93123b6531961ea0fddc1.webm?t=1772009947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195580/extras/ea7621ae89a93123b6531961ea0fddc1.mp4?t=1772009947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你发现了一位2000年代初年轻女孩的笔记本电脑。莉莉是典型的十几岁女孩——戏剧性、情绪化、有远大的梦想——但她隐藏着一个秘密。与她的老朋友重新联系，阅读她令人发囧的博客，并解决解开她过去的部分谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然她的电脑一开始看起来很普通，但当有人意识到你不是莉莉时，一切都改变了......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195580/extras/7f9b4d58658077ebdc5b15eeeccd7c29.poster.avif?t=1772009947\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195580/extras/7f9b4d58658077ebdc5b15eeeccd7c29.webm?t=1772009947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195580/extras/7f9b4d58658077ebdc5b15eeeccd7c29.mp4?t=1772009947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特征：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >早期的互联网又回来了。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要你探索莉莉世界的谜题。查看一切：她的笔记本电脑文件、社交媒体、日记——甚至是你自己的电脑。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真正的畏惧。所有游戏内照片均取自开发者（或她的朋友）青少年时期的自己。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关于作为一个孤独的书呆子成长的人物丰富的故事。</p></li></ul>",
